```

## ES6 Modules (import/export)
```javascript
// math.mjs
export const sum = (a, b) => a + b;
export const multiply = (a, b) => a * b;

// app.mjs
import { sum, multiply } from './math.mjs';
console.log(sum(5, 3)); // 8
```

